[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    463[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 15.4 (Sepsis Treatment Optimization):** Same offline RL framework applied to a different ICU decision problem. Shares the state construction and safety filtering patterns.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    464[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Recipe 15.6 (Glucose Control in ICU):** Another sequential ICU decision problem with continuous action spaces and tight safety constraints.
